Project,Insight,is,a,provider,of,mid,market,project,management,software,Features,include,portfolio,project,and,resource,management,and,collaboration,The,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,Project,Insight,with,their,own,applications,Data,exposed,by,the,API,includes,company,custom,fields,invoices,projects,reference,time,billing,and,users,The,API,uses,SOAP,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,Full,documentation,is,not,publicly,available